actions.text: Called up by House by Unanimous Consent.
Resolution Agreed to in House by Voice Vote.
Received in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Voice Vote.

official_title: A concurrent resolution requesting the President to return the enrolled bill (H.R. 3003) relating to the conveyance of certain land located in the State of Maryland to the Maryland National Capital Park and Planning Commission and providing for its reenrollment with technical corrections.

summary.text: Requests the President to return the enrolled bill H.R. 3003 (relating to the conveyance of land in Maryland) for its reenrollment with technical corrections.

titles.title: A concurrent resolution requesting the President to return the enrolled bill (H.R. 3003) relating to the conveyance of certain land located in the State of Maryland to the Maryland National Capital Park and Planning Commission and providing for its reenrollment with technical corrections.
